com.bitplan.exp

Class ExpBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bitplan.exp.ExpBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExpListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class ExpBaseListener
extends Object
implements ExpListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of ExpListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
